Let the Design Toscano Ring Around the Rosie Dancing Little Girls Statue frolic in play to the delight of your guests. This fine statue is made from resin but you wouldn't believe it with the faux-stone finish. These little girls are forever caught in time playing to their hearts' content. About Design Toscano Design Toscano is the country's premier source for statues and other historical and antique replicas, which are available through the company's catalog and website. Design Toscano's founders, Michael and Marilyn Stopka, created Design Toscano in 1990. While on a trip to Paris, the Stopkas first saw the marvelous carvings of gargoyles and water spouts at the Notre Dame Cathedral. Inspired by the beauty and mystery of these pieces, they decided to introduce the world of medieval gargoyles to America in 1993. On a later trip to Albi, France, the Stopkas had the pleasure of being exposed to the world of Jacquard tapestries that they added quickly to the growing catalog. Since then, the company's product line has grown to include Egyptian, Medieval and other period pieces that are now among the current favorites of Design Toscano customers, along with an extensive collection of garden fountains, statuary, authentic canvas replicas of oil painting masterpieces, and other antique art reproductions. At Design Toscano, attention to detail is important. Travel directly to the source for all historical replicas ensures brilliant design. Cast in fine-quality designer resin. Features 3 little girls in different pose. Hand finished sculpture for a realistic appearance. Perfect accent for your pool or pond. Dimensions: 24W x 6D x 12H in..<div id=""shipping_info"">

About Design Toscano: Design Toscano is the country's premier source for statues and other historical and antique replicas, which are available through the company's catalog and website. Design Toscano's founders, Michael and Marilyn Stopka, created Design Toscano in 1990. While on a trip to Paris, the Stopkas first saw the marvelous carvings of gargoyles and water spouts at the Notre Dame Cathedral. Inspired by the beauty and mystery of these pieces, they decided to introduce the world of medieval gargoyles to America in 1993. On a later trip to Albi, France, the Stopkas had the pleasure of being exposed to the world of Jacquard tapestries that they added quickly to the growing catalog. Since then, the company's product line has grown to include Egyptian, Medieval and other period pieces that are now among the current favorites of Design Toscano customers, along with an extensive collection of garden fountains, statuary, authentic canvas replicas of oil painting masterpieces, and other antique art reproductions. At Design Toscano, attention to detail is important. Travel directly to the source for all historical replicas ensures brilliant design. Stunning rooster that's great for farmhouses. Dark humor perfect for a garden only you could create. Tuck the Design Toscano Sinister Simon Giant Skull Sculpture between your nightshade and wolfs bane plants and let the gothic drama unfold. This ferocious, oversized scull is artfully carved of resin and can withstand life outdoors easily. It has amazing detail accentuated by an antiqued faux stone finish. About Design Toscano Design Toscano is the country's premier source for statues and other historical and antique replicas, which are available through the company's catalog and website. Design Toscano's founders, Michael and Marilyn Stopka, created Design Toscano in 1990. While on a trip to Paris, the Stopkas first saw the marvelous carvings of gargoyles and water spouts at the Notre Dame Cathedral. Inspired by the beauty and mystery of these pieces, they decided to introduce the world of medieval gargoyles to America in 1993. On a later trip to Albi, France, the Stopkas had the pleasure of being exposed to the world of Jacquard tapestries that they added quickly to the growing catalog. Since then, the company's product line has grown to include Egyptian, Medieval and other period pieces that are now among the current favorites of Design Toscano customers, along with an extensive collection of garden fountains, statuary, authentic canvas replicas of oil painting masterpieces, and other antique art reproductions. At Design Toscano, attention to detail is important. Travel directly to the source for all historical replicas ensures brilliant design. High-quality designer resin construction. About Design Toscano: Design Toscano is the country's premier source for statues and other historical and antique replicas, which are available through the company's catalog and website. Design Toscano's founders, Michael and Marilyn Stopka, created Design Toscano in 1990. While on a trip to Paris, the Stopkas first saw the marvelous carvings of gargoyles and water spouts at the Notre Dame Cathedral. Inspired by the beauty and mystery of these pieces, they decided to introduce the world of medieval gargoyles to America in 1993. On a later trip to Albi, France, the Stopkas had the pleasure of being exposed to the world of Jacquard tapestries that they added quickly to the growing catalog. Since then, the company's product line has grown to include Egyptian, Medieval and other period pieces that are now among the current favorites of Design Toscano customers, along with an extensive collection of garden fountains, statuary, authentic canvas replicas of oil painting masterpieces, and other antique art reproductions. At Design Toscano, attention to detail is important. Travel directly to the source for all historical replicas ensures brilliant design. Made of solid cast iron. Hand-painted finish. Dimensions: 13W x 7.5D x 7.5H in.. Use as doorstop or yard decor.<div id=""shipping_info"">

About Design ToscanoDesign Toscano is the country's premier source for statues and other historical and antique replicas, which are available through the company's catalog and website. Design Toscano's founders, Michael and Marilyn Stopka, created Design Toscano in 1990. While on a trip to Paris, the Stopkas first saw the marvelous carvings of gargoyles and water spouts at the Notre Dame Cathedral. Since then, the company's product line has grown to include Egyptian, Medieval and other period pieces that are now among the current favorites of Design Toscano customers, along with an extensive collection of garden fountains, statuary, authentic canvas replicas of oil painting masterpieces, and other antique art reproductions. Such a graceful and majestic creature of old. The Design Toscano The Enchanted Unicorn Sculpture will add a magical touch to your garden. The elegant design of this unicorn sculpture features a realistic stone finish. Built for years to come, this statue is crafted from high-quality resin. A must-have accent piece for your garden or yard. About Design Toscano Design Toscano is the country's premier source for statues and other historical and antique replicas, which are available through the company's catalog and website. Design Toscano's founders, Michael and Marilyn Stopka, created Design Toscano in 1990. While on a trip to Paris, the Stopkas first saw the marvelous carvings of gargoyles and water spouts at the Notre Dame Cathedral. Inspired by the beauty and mystery of these pieces, they decided to introduce the world of medieval gargoyles to America in 1993. On a later trip to Albi, France, the Stopkas had the pleasure of being exposed to the world of Jacquard tapestries that they added quickly to the growing catalog. Since then, the company's product line has grown to include Egyptian, Medieval and other period pieces that are now among the current favorites of Design Toscano customers, along with an extensive collection of garden fountains, statuary, authentic canvas replicas of oil painting masterpieces, and other antique art reproductions. At Design Toscano, attention to detail is important. Travel directly to the source for all historical replicas ensures brilliant design. Crafted from high-quality resin. 商品説明
「お花のポケット 園芸用 1ポケットタイプ 5シート入り N-2388 グレー」は、フェンス・門扉・ラティス等をキレイな草花等で飾れる園芸グッズです。そのまま植物を栽培でき、直接・園芸用培養土を入れてご使用いただけます。通気性があり、水分も必要なとき以外のものは排出してくれるので、植物の成長に適した環境を作ってくれます。(根腐れの心配も緩和されます)
使用方法
●フェンス・門扉・ラティスなどへの「ハトメ」の穴で市販の「Sフック」「結束バンド」などを使用して固定してください。
●通常の鉢植えを行うように、ポケット部に園芸用培養土を直接入れて植え替えを行ってください。
●本商品は通気性があり、水分も通常の鉢同様に必要以上に与えたお水は外部に排出します。
●注意：本商品は通気性が良いので培養土の乾きを防ぐため、土の水分状態をご確認の上こまめな水分補充を行ってください。※季節や本商品を設置される環境によって、水分の保たれる状態は違いますので状況に応じて適した水分補充を行いましょう。
使用上の注意
●火気の周辺でのご使用は絶対におやめください。
●本商品は食べられません、お子様がお口に入れないようご注意ください。
●培養土に保つ事が可能な水分量以上の物は外部に排出されるので、本商品を設置される下部分のスペースは水漏れには十分注意を払ってください。(水漏れ厳禁などの物は置かないように気をつけてください。)
●台風や強風時は、風を受けて外れる恐れがあります。一時収納を行う等十分注意を払ってください。
●草花や園芸用培養土以外の物をポケット部に詰めないでください。
●目安として1kg以上の物をポケット部に詰めないでください。
●目安として1kgまでの物をポケット部に詰める事は可能ですが、本商品を取り付けられる対象物(フェンス・壁・門扉など)の強度も合わせてご確認の上、取り扱いには十分注意を払ってください。
●商品改良のため、予告なく仕様を変更する場合があります。
